<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>昱通實頁股份有限公司｜房屋租賃管理中心</title>

  <style>
    :root {
      --yellow: #eac85f;
      --yellow-soft: #f6e6aa;
      --mori-yellow: #d8c58a;
      --cream: #faf7ef;
      --beige: #eee7dc;
      --brown: #6f6048;
      --text: #3f3a33;
      --white: #fffdf8;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      font-family: "Noto Serif TC", "Noto Sans TC", "Microsoft JhengHei", serif;
      background: var(--cream);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.9;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    header {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      width: 100%;
      z-index: 999;
      background: rgba(250, 247, 239, 0.88);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(216, 197, 138, 0.25);
    }

    .nav {
      max-width: 1180px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 18px 28px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--brown);
    }

    .logo {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--yellow), var(--yellow-soft));
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      color: white;
      font-size: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(216, 197, 138, 0.35);
    }

    nav ul {
      display: flex;
      gap: 28px;
      list-style: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--brown);
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: #b99a38;
    }

    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 150px 28px 80px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      background:
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(250,247,239,0.94) 0%, rgba(250,247,239,0.72) 48%, rgba(250,247,239,0.25) 100%),
        url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600585154340-be6161a56a0c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80") center/cover;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -1px;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 150px;
      background: var(--cream);
      clip-path: ellipse(70% 45% at 50% 100%);
    }

    .hero-content {
      max-width: 1180px;
      margin: auto;
      width: 100%;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .hero-label {
      color: #b99a38;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 68px);
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.35;
      color: var(--brown);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .hero p {
      max-width: 640px;
      font-size: clamp(17px, 2vw, 22px);
      color: #5f564b;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 42px;
      padding: 13px 34px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--yellow);
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(216, 197, 138, 0.45);
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      background: #d5b34b;
    }

    section {
      padding: 100px 28px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1180px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    .section-title {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 58px;
    }

    .section-title span {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #b99a38;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    }

    .section-title h2 {
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--brown);
    }

    .about-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
      gap: 60px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .about-img {
      min-height: 470px;
      border-radius: 46% 54% 48% 52%;
      background:
        linear-gradient(rgba(246,230,170,0.18), rgba(246,230,170,0.18)),
        url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600607687939-ce8a6c25118c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80") center/cover;
      box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(111,96,72,0.12);
    }

    .about-text {
      background: var(--white);
      padding: 52px;
      border-radius: 34px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(111,96,72,0.08);
    }

    .about-text p + p {
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .services {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--cream), var(--beige));
    }

    .service-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 26px;
    }

    .service-card {
      background: var(--white);
      padding: 42px 28px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 32px;
      transition: 0.3s;
      border: 1px solid rgba(216, 197, 138, 0.28);
    }

    .service-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(111,96,72,0.12);
    }

    .icon {
      width: 76px;
      height: 76px;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--yellow-soft);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-size: 32px;
      color: var(--brown);
    }

    .service-card h3 {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--brown);
    }

    .contact {
      background:
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(250,247,239,0.96), rgba(250,247,239,0.82)),
        url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600566753190-17f0baa2a6c3?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80") center/cover;
    }

    .contact-box {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: auto;
      background: rgba(255,253,248,0.92);
      padding: 56px;
      border-radius: 36px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 22px 55px rgba(111,96,72,0.12);
    }

    .contact-box h2 {
      color: var(--brown);
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .address {
      margin-top: 24px;
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #5f564b;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 34px 20px;
      background: var(--yellow);
      color: white;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .fade {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
      transition: 0.8s ease;
    }

    .fade.show {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav {
        padding: 14px 20px;
      }

      nav ul {
        display: none;
      }

      .hero {
        padding-top: 130px;
        background-position: center;
      }

      section {
        padding: 76px 22px;
      }

      .about-grid,
      .service-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .about-img {
        min-height: 330px;
      }

      .about-text,
      .contact-box {
        padding: 34px 26px;
      }

      .section-title h2 {
        font-size: 28px;
      }

      .service-card {
        padding: 36px 24px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <div class="nav">
      <a href="#home" class="brand">
        <div class="logo">昱</div>
        <span>房屋租賃管理中心</span>
      </a>

      <nav>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#home">首頁</a></li>
          <li><a href="#about">關於我們</a></li>
          <li><a href="#services">營業項目</a></li>
          <li><a href="#contact">公司地址</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section id="home" class="hero">
      <div class="hero-content fade">
        <div class="hero-label">HOUSE RENTAL MANAGEMENT CENTER</div>
        <h1>昱通實頁股份有限公司</h1>
        <p>
          用心守護日常，延續家的溫度。<br>
          我們以真誠相伴，隨時等候您安心回家。
        </p>
        <a href="#about" class="btn">了解更多</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title fade">
          <span>ABOUT US</span>
          <h2>關於我們</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="about-grid">
          <div class="about-img fade"></div>

          <div class="about-text fade">
            <p>
              我們深信，建築因為有了人的氣息，才真正成為「家」。
              我們將「有溫度的服務」融入日常的每一個細節中，
              致力於為每一位住戶打造最深刻的歸屬感。
            </p>

            <p>
              從清晨踏出大門時親切的一句早安，到深夜為您點亮的那盞大廳暖燈，
              我們把每一次的互動都當作對家人的照顧。
            </p>

            <p>
              不論是細心核對為您代收的包裹，或是即時協助解決生活中的修繕大小事，
              我們都在背後默默為您撐起堅實的安全網，讓您生活得絕對安心。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="services" class="services">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title fade">
          <span>SERVICE</span>
          <h2>營業項目</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="service-grid">
          <div class="service-card fade">
            <div class="icon">🏠</div>
            <h3>租賃</h3>
            <p>提供穩定、安心、具溫度的房屋租賃管理服務。</p>
          </div>

          <div class="service-card fade">
            <div class="icon">🅿️</div>
            <h3>停車塔</h3>
            <p>協助停車空間管理，提升日常使用便利與安全性。</p>
          </div>

          <div class="service-card fade">
            <div class="icon">🌿</div>
            <h3>住宅</h3>
            <p>以細膩服務維護居住品質，讓住戶安心回家。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="contact">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="contact-box fade">
          <span>ADDRESS</span>
          <h2>公司地址</h2>
          <p class="address">台北市大同區太原路4樓之2</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    © 2026 昱通實頁股份有限公司 All Rights Reserved.
  </footer>

  <script>
    const fadeElements = document.querySelectorAll(".fade");

    const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
      entries => {
        entries.forEach(entry => {
          if (entry.isIntersecting) {
            entry.target.classList.add("show");
          }
        });
      },
      {
        threshold: 0.15
      }
    );

    fadeElements.forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
  </script>
</body>
</html>
